headline: Traders Brace For Swings Following Tesla Earnings
summary: Traders are girding themselves for a big move in Tesla shares after the electric-vehicle maker's quarterly results due Wednesday afternoon. The options market is pricing in a roughly 7% swing, higher or lower, in Tesla's stock in the session following earnings, show Option Research & Technology Services data.

headline: CME Group Q3 Earnings Surpass Estimates, Revenues Decline Y/Y
summary: CME's third-quarter results reflect declining revenues due to lower clearing and transaction fees and other, as well as lower trading volumes.
